Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like doing this to such old folks,\Nbut you're very important witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be in trouble if you died or ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barricaded the back door and\Nthe windows with furniture.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they really wanted to, it wouldn't\Nbe too hard for them to break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go down to the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how to fire a gun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.00,0:00:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd hate it if anything happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to survive and tell everyone everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wim. Stay in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong ally is coming to save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.57,0:01:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're in a pinch, no matter where\Nyou are, he'll come and save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll punish any wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the invincible Magnificent Steiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:03.82,Monster-Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Wrath of the Magnificent Steiner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go north along the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the children can make it out safely from here on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't checked the center of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to me. You have to lead the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know a man named Bonaparta, no, Klaus Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's the owner of the Versteck Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. I'm a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are bodies everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I run to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you run from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Him. He was giving orders from the hotel room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto! I thought it was weird that he\Nkept on going in and out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time he came back, he took\Na shower and changed clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In a room on the 4th floor of the Bergbach Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:05:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought he was like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a bunch of people hiding at the Versteck Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get there by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,On my own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The illusion has finally become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:06:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that you are here, the vacation I took to pull\Nthe threads of that illusion together is now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,As of now, I'm on duty as an officer of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've been on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The man you're after is at the Versteck Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I make it back, I want to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of questions I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,are running through my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The memory in the farthest recesses of my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your deepest memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If Johan has this memory... If he can remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the man who's giving the orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you where Roberto is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it. There are bodies everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go insane if I stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we have to get to the Versteck Hotel as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.81,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's your wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous here. Let's go somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me have your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kill the guy who shot Erika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who ruined my life... I'm going to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife wouldn't have wanted that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.34,0:10:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife would have wanted you to keep your child safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a route by the north road\Nthat will lead you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should forget about the hotel and take the road as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be back. Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So they aren't after our lotto winnings at all, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.82,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These last few days have been a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I really went crazy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought all these guns because of that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal life is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell my wife that this isn't our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hennig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hennig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Hennig!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're shooting from the building across the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a basement in this hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a storage room under the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be asking you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad's doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad ran out of alcohol and went mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:13:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like when he beats me up. He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'd go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It will end if I give myself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say that again, I'll tie you up down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.94,0:13:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come up with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm in trouble, the invincible Magnificent Steiner will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen some cases of experiments like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After experiencing overwhelming rage, grief, or intense stress,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,different personalities would appear in the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Such children tended to be extremely violent, but many of them committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well to live this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a second and let's talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's giving the orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you were former Stasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.71,0:14:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not from anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen with your own ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take orders. Listen to your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Think with your own mind about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared, but I made it here by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent Steiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}Are you gathered around the tube, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyday, I watched TV intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}What adventure awaits us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no memory of the final episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\a6}If you're in trouble, call out his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lets go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that weak young man ever realize that he turned\Ninto the Magnificent Steiner whenever he got angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that young man live happily ever after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that young man... live happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go just a little farther, we'll be out of these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Ruhenheim, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's happening in the town, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many armed men in the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole town has turned into a blood bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see an oriental Japanese man with long hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he helped us escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed behind to try and save the other people in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was headed to the Versteck Hotel when we parted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My car is parked at the end of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it to take the injured to a hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and contact the authorities as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you headed to town? You shouldn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, that Asian man, is my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to save him. Please hurry and call the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Versteck Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.36,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Two in the other building, one on the floor below us, and one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I got four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Magnificent Steiner appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it with my own anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, those wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Before I forget, take this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it from Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he found it at the Red Rose Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's headed to the Bergbach Hotel by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take care of you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let me rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Wim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been raining for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be much nicer here if it cleared up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.09,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When it gets sunny out, let's take Wim on a picnic together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have good wine and good cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sad that I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finally sad that my child died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't lose their emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotions just wandered around in an unknown place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a letter that was addressed to\Nme decades ago has finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true sadness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the final episode of the Magnificent Steiner,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he became human again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Grimmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
